run(sql="
with cte as(
select distinct a.date, 
                a.pogId, 
                a.subOrderId, 
                a.CPT, 
                a.Channels, 
                a.NM3SO,
                case when b.availability = 'in stock' then 'IS'
                               else 'OS'
                               end as Stock, 
                case when lower(b.customLabel2) like '%cpt1%' then 'CPT1'
                               else 'No_CPT1'
                               end as CPT1,
                case when lower(b.customLabel2) like '%sale%' then 'Sale'
                               else 'No_Sale'
                               end as Sale
from(
     select distinct a.subOrderId, 
                     a.pogId, 
                     a.CPT, 
                     a.Channels, 
                     a.date, 
                     b.NM3SO 
     from(
          select distinct a.subOrderId, 
                          b.pogId, 
                          case when lower(a.utmContent) like '%cpt%' then 'CPT'
                               else 'No_CPT'
                               end as CPT,
                          case when lower(a.Channel) like 'fb%' then 'FB'
                               else 'Others'
                               end as Channels,
                          a.orderDate as date 
          from `temp.order_sd_2` a 
          left join `last3Days(agCmDump)` b 
          on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
          where a.orderDate in ('2023-04-11','2023-04-04','2023-04-05','2023-04-06')
        ) a
     left join `temp.nmso_bau` b 
     on a.pogId=b.pogId
) a
left join `temp.FB_Live_New_Feed` b
on a.pogId=b.dmPublisherInfoId
)

select distinct date, 
                count(distinct subOrderId) as SD_Orders, 
                count(distinct case when Channels='FB' then subOrderId end) as FB_Orders,
                count(distinct case when Channels='FB' and CPT='CPT' then subOrderId end) as FB_CPT_Orders 
from cte 
where Stock='IS' and NM3SO>25 and NM3SO<=30 
group by date
order by date
",1000)
